==== 2013-14球季 ==== 
2013年8月18日，英超球會修咸頓簽入奧斯華度，並簽下一份四年合約，轉會費約近一千四百萬[[歐元|歐元]]，年薪二百萬。<ref>{{cite news |title=Saints sign Osvaldo |url=http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/saints-sign-osvaldo-1000668.aspx |publisher=Southampton FC |date=2013-08-18 |accessdate=2013-08-25 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818190457/http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/saints-sign-osvaldo-1000668.aspx |archive-date=2013-08-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>6天後，奧斯華度在修咸頓主場對[[新特蘭|新特蘭]]的英超聯賽中上陣，下半場開始時後備入替防守中場[[摩根·舒尼達連|舒拉達連]]，成為他加盟修咸頓後的首場比賽<ref>{{cite news |title=Southampton 1-1 Sunderland |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23737155 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2013-08-24 |accessdate=2013-08-25 |language=en |archive-date=2016-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118123550/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23737155 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
